  "instructions": [
    "Mix fenugreek leaves, cheeese, tapioca flour, and salt in a bowl.",
    "Add coconut oil, vinegar, and black pepper to the bowl and mix until a dough forms.",
    "Knead the dough for 5-7 minutes until it's smooth and elastic.",
    "Shape the dough into small balls, about 1 inch in diameter.",
    "Heat a non-stick skillet or frying pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Cook the balls in batches, flattening them slightly, for 3-4 minutes on each side until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!",
